---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <Nav />
  <main class="pt-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-geist font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

        <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-geist font-medium mt-8 mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p>amics values your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-geist font-medium mt-8 mb-4">2. Data We Collect</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
            <li>Personal Information: Name, phone number, and preferences provided during signup.</li>
            <li>Call Data: Recordings of calls for quality assurance and improvement purposes.</li>
            <li>Usage Data: Information about how you interact with our Services.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-geist font-medium mt-8 mb-4">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
            <li>To provide personalized check-in calls.</li>
            <li>To improve our Services through analysis of call recordings.</li>
            <li>To communicate updates or issues related to our Services.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-geist font-medium mt-8 mb-4">4. Call Recording</h2>
          <p>We may record calls to improve service quality. These recordings are securely stored and accessed only by authorized personnel.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-geist font-medium mt-8 mb-4">5. Sharing Your Data</h2>
          <p>We do not sell your data. We may share data with service providers to maintain and improve our Services, subject to strict confidentiality.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-geist font-medium mt-8 mb-4">6. Data Security</h2>
          <p>We implement measures to protect your data from unauthorized access. However, no system is completely secure.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-geist font-medium mt-8 mb-4">7. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to access, modify, or delete your personal data. Contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@amics.ai" class="text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-800">hello@amics.ai</a> for assistance.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-geist font-medium mt-8 mb-4">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Continued use of the Services signifies acceptance of changes.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-geist font-medium mt-8 mb-4">9. Contact</h2>
          <p>If you have concerns or questions, reach out to us at <a href="mailto:hello@amics.ai" class="text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-800">hello@amics.ai</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout> 